    <amendmentBody>
      <amendmentContent>
        <block name="amendment">
          <p>It is proposed to amend <ref href="/akn/poc/act/valencian-paella-recipe#art_11">Article 11</ref> to make the socarrat optional:</p>
          <p><mod>"Article 11. Socarrat and presentation. Optionally, during the last 2 minutes the heat may be raised to form the socarrat. The paella may be served in the pan or plated according to preference."</mod></p>
        </block>
        <block name="justification">
          <p>Burnt socarrat is the leading cause of rejection among diners unfamiliar with the dish. Making it optional increases the accessibility of the recipe.</p>
        </block>
      </amendmentContent>
    </amendmentBody>
